  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Wayland</title>

    <para>
      <application>Wayland</application> is a project to define a protocol
      for a compositor to talk to its clients as well as a library
      implementation of the protocol.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

